Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:10.75,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:17.21,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
